        <text>
            <body>
                
                                        <p>Ego, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324640" xml:id="d1e134067">Hugo, Dei gratia
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324435" xml:id="d1e134069">Autissiodorensis</placeName> episcopus</persName>, notum volo fieri
                        tam presentibus quam futuris quod <persName key="d1e12670" xml:id="d1e134073">Stephanus <addName>Rufus</addName>
                        </persName>, frater <persName key="d1e12676" xml:id="d1e134078">Johannis
                            Beruardi</persName>, <lb n="2"/> vendidit vineam suam magnam que est in
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324961" xml:id="d1e134083">Monte
                            Reifridi</placeName> monachis de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e134087">Fonteneto</orgName>. Concesserunt autem monachi illi
                            prefa<lb n="3" break="no"/>to <persName key="d1e12682" xml:id="d1e134092">Johanni</persName> ut vineam illam possideat idem
                            <persName key="d1e12688" xml:id="d1e134095">Johannes</persName> toto
                        tempore vite sue nisi secularibus abrenuntiare voluerit, sub hac <lb n="4"/>
                        tamen conditione quod prefatus <persName key="d1e12695" xml:id="d1e134100">Johannes</persName> annuatim reddet unum modium vini monachis
                        prescriptis quod tempore messium <lb n="5"/> bibent. Reddet etiam eis
                            <num>xv</num> denarios de censu singulis annis ut per hec ab eis
                        possideri vinea cognoscatur post deces<lb n="6" break="no"/>sum tamen
                            <persName key="d1e12701" xml:id="d1e134111">Johannis</persName>.
                            <persName key="d1e12707" xml:id="d1e134114">Johannes</persName> vero
                        propter hoc donum eisdem monachis domum suam que est sita super aquam
                        concessit possi<lb n="7" break="no"/>dendam de cetero ad omnes voluntates
                        suas explendas. Hec vidimus fieri et audivimus et in hujus facti testimonium
                        ad <lb n="8"/> petitionem monachorum et <persName key="d1e12713" xml:id="d1e134122">Johannis</persName> et <persName key="d1e12719" xml:id="d1e134125">Stephani</persName> presenti scripto sigilli nostri
                        munimen apposuimus. Datum anno incarnationis Dominice <lb n="9"/> .M°. c°.
                        lxxx. <figure rend="trait"/>.iii°.</p>
                
